<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi>viracoḻatevaṉeṉ Emakkuccellāniṉṟa yāṇṭu nālāvatu Avināciyāṇṭār tā
<lb n="2" break="no"/>ṉattilum maṟṟum Innāyanār tevatāṉamāy Uḷḷa Ūrkaḷilumirukkum civappirāmaṇar tevaraṭiyār <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> kku Iṟuttu
<lb n="3"/>Iruntavaruntavanaṭai kāṉappeṟu Avināci Āḷuṭaiyāṟku tirumeṟpūccukku Utakapūrvamākak kuṭuttom <unclear>nintamā</unclear>eppeṟpaṭṭā<note n="122-1">This is written in continuation of the end of another inscription.</note> 
